<plot>Chasing Rainbows: Young Adults Living with Cancer is a documentary built around a living-room conversation between six young adults: four women and two men. With passion and humor, they discuss hope, fear, faith, sexuality, infertility, family relationships, finances, the future and more. Their stories are an invaluable source of information, inspiration and hope - not only for other young adults facing life-threatening illness, but also for their families, friends, caregivers and medical support teams.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?100728</url></doc>
